Bedroom renovation plan:

-Choose wall and ceiling paint colour
-Buy paint colour samples
-Paint the wall with samples and choose the perfect colour 
-Calculate wall and ceiling painting area
-Buy the right amount of paint and painting accessories like:
  -masking tape
  -foil to cover furniture
  -painting rollers
-Get everything out of the room, or move everything and cover it all with foil
-Remove sockets and skirting boards
-Protect everything with masking tape
-Paint the ceiling two times
-When the last layer of the ceiling paint is dry, protect the ceiling edge with masking tape
-Paint the walls (two layers if necessary)
-Wait until the wall paint is dry
-Remove the protection and screw the skirting boards and sockets
-Set everything (furniture, decorations etc) back up
